popover' data-placement='top'>يَوۡمَ ٱلۡحَجِّ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرِ</a> أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ بَرِيٓءٞ مِّنَ </div><div>ٱلۡمُشۡرِكِينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَرَسُولُهُۥۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَإِن تُبۡتُمۡ فَهُوَ خَيۡرٞ لَّكُمۡۖ وَإِن تَوَلَّيۡتُمۡ </div><div>فَٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَنَّكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> غَيۡرُ مُعۡجِزِي ٱللَّهِۗ وَبَشِّرِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ بِعَذَابٍ </div><div>أَلِيمٍ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٣</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ عَٰهَدتُّم مِّنَ ٱلۡمُشۡرِكِينَ ثُمَّ <a data-content='لم ينقضوا عهدكم بل وفّوا به' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لَمۡ يَنقُصُوكُمۡ</a> </div><div>شَيۡ‍ٔٗا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='لم يُعاونوا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَلَمۡ يُظَٰهِرُواْ</a> عَلَيۡكُمۡ أَحَدٗا فَأَتِمُّوٓاْ إِلَيۡهِمۡ عَهۡدَهُمۡ إِلَىٰ مُدَّتِهِمۡۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>مُدَّتِهِمۡۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>إِنَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱللَّهَ يُحِبُّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ ٤ فَإِذَا <a data-content='انقضت أشهر العهد الأربعة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱنسَلَخَ ٱلۡأَشۡهُرُ</a> </div><div>ٱلۡحُرُمُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فَٱقۡتُلُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡمُشۡرِكِينَ حَيۡثُ وَجَدتُّم